text: Siphamandla Krweqe (born 6 October 2000) is a South African cricketer. He made his List A debut for Border in the 2018–19 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge on 30 March 2019. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Border cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
